5 (2) IC 21-27-4-5;
6 (3) IC 21-27-5-5;
7 (4) IC 21-27-7-7; and
8 (5) IC 21-27-8-8;
9 the commission shall determine a tuition rate and mandatory fee
10 cost of living adjustment based on the Consumer Price Index as
11 prepared by the United States Department of Labor.
