13 AS A NEW SECTION TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE JULY
14 1, 2026]: Sec. 6. (a) For purposes of this section, an undergraduate
15 student includes a student enrolled in:
16 (1) a bachelor's degree program; or
17 (2) any degree program or specialized degree program that is
